Package: ggsegAAL
Title: AAL Atlases for the 'ggseg' Ecosystem
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Athanasia Mo", "Mowinckel",
           email = "a.m.mowinckel@psykologi.uio.no",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5756-0223")),
    person("Herve", "Lemaitre",
           email = "herve.lemaitre@u-bordeaux.fr",
           role = "ctb",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5952-076X")))
Description: AAL (Automated Anatomical Labeling) atlases for the 'ggseg'
    ecosystem. Provides unified 'ggseg_atlas' objects for AAL2 (cortical,
    Rolls et al. 2015) and AAL3 (cortical, subcortical, cerebellum,
    Rolls et al. 2020), with both 2D polygon geometry and 3D vertex/mesh
    data for use with 'ggseg' and 'ggseg3d'.
